summary: Replaces English road signs with Polish. Plus blank road signs
descriptionHtml:
New version [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=800]hear[/url]

Replaces English road signs with Polish. Plus blank road signs.

ver. 1.0

Installation:
Copy and paste Data folder to \\skyrim\\ folder
To uninstall:
Navigate to skyrim\\Data\\textures\\clutter\\signage\\roadsigns and delete roadsignscities01, roadsignscities01_n, roadsignsnorthern01, roadsignsnorthern01_n, roadsignssouthern01, roadsignssouthern01_n
author: SirYoggi
